HEADWORD: Tackled
<hw>Tac"kled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Made of ropes tacked
together.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My man shall be with thee,⟦br⟧
And bring thee cords made like a <qex>tackled</qex> stair.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tackling</ent>⟦br⟧
